{
  "ep": "26",
  "title": "パンダくんの願い",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "audio": 0,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "ほほう…　半田さんがね",
          "en": "Oh... Handasan, you say."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 1,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "なんで　はっきり言わないのかな？",
          "en": "I wonder why he doesn't say it clearly."
        },
        {
          "ja": "半田さんは　奥手だしね",
          "en": "Handa is a bit shy, you know."
        },
        {
          "ja": "そうなの？",
          "en": "Is that so?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 2,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "雑誌なんかで知識は豊富そうだけど",
          "en": "He seems to have a wealth of knowledge from magazines and such, though."
        },
        {
          "ja": "いざとなるとてんで勇気が出ないタイプだね",
          "en": "When it comes down to it, he's the type who can't muster any courage at all."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 3,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "あぁ　知ってる",
          "en": "Ah, I know."
        },
        {
          "ja": "えっと…　たしか耳年寄り？",
          "en": "Um... if I remember correctly, isn't it \"an old head on young shoulders\"?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "ツッコみづらい間違え方しないでよ",
          "en": "Don't make mistakes that are hard to joke about."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 4,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "半田さんにアドバイスしたいんだけど 何かない？",
          "en": "I want to give Handa some advice, but do you have any suggestions?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "こっちに振るの？",
          "en": "Are you passing this to me?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 5,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "だって　常勤パンダさん経験豊富でしょ？",
          "en": "But you're an experienced full-time panda, right?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "バツ２だし",
          "en": "I've been divorced twice."
        },
        {
          "ja": "勝手に　バツ２にしないでって 言ったでしょ",
          "en": "I told you not to assume I'm divorced twice."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 6,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "でもさ",
          "en": "But still,"
        },
        {
          "ja": "僕らってカップルに関しては目が肥えてるよね",
          "en": "We're pretty sharp when it comes to couples, aren't we?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "あぁ　それは確かにね",
          "en": "Ah, that's certainly true."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 7,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "ここに来るお客さんは カップル多いもんね",
          "en": "There are a lot of couples among the customers who come here, aren't there?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "そうだね",
          "en": "Yeah, that's true."
        },
        {
          "ja": "初デートのカップルなんてういういしいよね",
          "en": "Couples on their first date are so adorable, aren't they?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 8,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "手を繋ぐことも できなかったりしてさ",
          "en": "They can't even hold hands or anything."
        },
        {
          "ja": "うん　うん",
          "en": "Yeah, yeah."
        },
        {
          "ja": "あとはケンカしてるカップルとかもいるよね",
          "en": "And then there are also couples who are fighting, right?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "こっちから見てても わかるっていうか",
          "en": "You can tell just by looking from over here."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 9,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "そう？",
          "en": "Really?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "ほら！こっちに来る あの２人は",
          "en": "Look! Those two coming this way."
        },
        {
          "ja": "今ちょっと気まずい感じだね",
          "en": "They seem a bit awkward right now."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 10,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "あぁ　本当だ",
          "en": "Oh, you're right."
        },
        {
          "ja": "でもね　見てなよ",
          "en": "But you know, just watch."
        },
        {
          "ja": "そこで　僕らを見つけると…",
          "en": "When they spot us there..."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 11,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "パンダだ",
          "en": "It's a panda."
        },
        {
          "ja": "あぁ　行こう",
          "en": "Ah, let's go."
        },
        {
          "ja": "わぁ～！　かわいい",
          "en": "Wow! So cute!"
        },
        {
          "ja": "ねっ？",
          "en": "Right?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "うん",
          "en": "Yeah"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 12,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "ねね　次はどこ行こっか",
          "en": "Hey, where should we go next?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "ほら！　仲直りした",
          "en": "Look! We made up."
        },
        {
          "ja": "常勤パンダさん　すご～い",
          "en": "Full-time Panda, you're amazing!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 13,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "そうかな？",
          "en": "Really?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "さすがは　ラテン系だね",
          "en": "As expected of the Latin type."
        },
        {
          "ja": "また　そんなキャラ付けする…",
          "en": "There you go, labeling me like that again..."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 14,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "アドバイス　お願いします！",
          "en": "Please give me some advice!"
        },
        {
          "ja": "ガテン系の常勤パンダさん",
          "en": "Full-time Panda, the blue-collar worker"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 15,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "だから　ツッコミづらいって…",
          "en": "That's why it's hard to make a comeback..."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 16,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "まぁ　アドバイスとしては",
          "en": "Well, as for advice..."
        },
        {
          "ja": "一歩前へ出るのが大事だね",
          "en": "Taking a step forward is important."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 17,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "どすこ～い！",
          "en": "Heave-ho!"
        },
        {
          "ja": "全然　恋の予感がしないよ？",
          "en": "I don't feel any hint of romance at all."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 18,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "相撲して どうするの",
          "en": "What are you going to do with sumo wrestling?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "しないの？",
          "en": "You're not going to?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "しないよ",
          "en": "I'm not going to."
        },
        {
          "ja": "なんにしても 恋は積極性が大事だね",
          "en": "In any case, being proactive is important in love, isn't it?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 19,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "説教くせぇか…",
          "en": "Does it sound preachy...?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "今また　変な想像したよね？",
          "en": "You just imagined something weird again, didn't you?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "積極性だよ？",
          "en": "Being proactive, right?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 20,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "お疲れさまでした",
          "en": "Good work today."
        },
        {
          "ja": "お疲れ～",
          "en": "See you later!"
        },
        {
          "ja": "お疲れさま",
          "en": "Take care."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 21,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "でさ…",
          "en": "So, you know..."
        },
        {
          "ja": "恋愛経験豊富な常勤パンダさんが",
          "en": "The full-time panda with plenty of romantic experience"
        },
        {
          "ja": "アドバイスくれたんだよ",
          "en": "Gave me some advice."
        },
        {
          "ja": "えっ",
          "en": "Huh?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 22,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "そうなの？",
          "en": "Is that so?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "気になる？",
          "en": "Are you curious?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "い…　いや…　別に",
          "en": "N... No... Not really."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 23,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "じゃあ　やめとく？",
          "en": "Then should I not tell you?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "えっ！　せ…　せっかくだから 一応聞くよ",
          "en": "Huh! W-well, since it's a good opportunity, I'll ask just in case."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 24,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "どうしたの？",
          "en": "What's wrong?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 25,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "でも　こんなものを飾って",
          "en": "But to display something like this..."
        },
        {
          "ja": "笹子さんに見られたら 恥ずかしいな…",
          "en": "It would be embarrassing if Sasako-san saw it..."
        },
        {
          "ja": "もう…　何悩んでるの？",
          "en": "Geez... What are you worrying about?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 26,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "ほら！　恋は積極性が大事！",
          "en": "Look! Being proactive is important in love!"
        },
        {
          "ja": "前に出る！",
          "en": "Step forward!"
        },
        {
          "ja": "パンダくん！",
          "en": "Panda-kun!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 27,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "こんにちは～",
          "en": "Hello~"
        },
        {
          "ja": "いらっしゃい あ",
          "en": "Welcome, ah."
        },
        {
          "ja": "パンダくん　半田さん",
          "en": "Panda-kun, Handa-san."
        },
        {
          "ja": "やっほ～",
          "en": "Hey there!"
        },
        {
          "ja": "おじゃまします",
          "en": "Excuse me for intruding."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 28,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "いいタイミングだね",
          "en": "Perfect timing!"
        },
        {
          "ja": "何が？",
          "en": "What do you mean?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "ちょうど 飾りつけが終わるところだよ",
          "en": "We're just finishing up the decorations."
        },
        {
          "ja": "これが　最後ね",
          "en": "This is the last one."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 29,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "僕が作った飾りだ～",
          "en": "These are the decorations I made!"
        },
        {
          "ja": "じゃあ　一番上に",
          "en": "Then, at the very top."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 30,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "今度は願いごとの短冊を つるしますよ～",
          "en": "Now let's hang the wish strips!"
        },
        {
          "ja": "皆さ～ん　どうぞ",
          "en": "Everyone, please go ahead."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 31,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "何　書いたの？",
          "en": "What did you write?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "見る？",
          "en": "Wanna see?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "Stop 地球温暖化",
          "en": "Stop global warming"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 32,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "切実だからね",
          "en": "It's a serious issue, after all."
        },
        {
          "ja": "僕のは　これ！",
          "en": "Mine is this!"
        },
        {
          "ja": "ペンこさんから告白されますように",
          "en": "I hope Penko confesses to me."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 33,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "ずうずうしいね",
          "en": "You're so bold."
        },
        {
          "ja": "どうしよう　告白されちゃったら！",
          "en": "What should I do if I get confessed to!"
        },
        {
          "ja": "困っちゃうよ　困っちゃうよ 困っちゃうよ…",
          "en": "I'd be in trouble, I'd be in trouble, I'd be in trouble..."
        },
        {
          "ja": "どっちなの？",
          "en": "Which one is it?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 34,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "半田さん お願い書いてきました？",
          "en": "Mr. Handa, did you write the request?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "あ　いや…",
          "en": "Ah, well..."
        },
        {
          "ja": "えっと…",
          "en": "Um..."
        },
        {
          "ja": "いや",
          "en": "No."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 35,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "その…",
          "en": "Um..."
        },
        {
          "ja": "恋は　積極性が大事",
          "en": "Love requires being proactive."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 36,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "書いてきました",
          "en": "I wrote it down."
        },
        {
          "ja": "じゃあ　つるしてください",
          "en": "Then, please hang it up."
        },
        {
          "ja": "はい",
          "en": "Yes."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 37,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "半田さん　彼女いないんですか？",
          "en": "Mr. Handa, do you not have a girlfriend?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "はい",
          "en": "Yes."
        },
        {
          "ja": "そうなんですか",
          "en": "Is that so?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "早くできるといいですね",
          "en": "I hope you find one soon."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 38,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "はい",
          "en": "Yes."
        },
        {
          "ja": "そろそろ締め切り",
          "en": "The deadline is approaching."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 39,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "パンダくん　願いごとつるした？",
          "en": "Panda-kun, did you hang up your wish?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 40,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "もう　忘れてたの？",
          "en": "Did you already forget?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "う～ん　どうしよう",
          "en": "Hmm, what should I do?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 41,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "えっと　足が長くなりますように",
          "en": "Um, I wish for my legs to become longer."
        },
        {
          "ja": "おこづかいアップ",
          "en": "An increase in allowance."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 42,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "テレビ出たい…",
          "en": "I want to be on TV..."
        },
        {
          "ja": "パンダくん",
          "en": "Panda-kun"
        },
        {
          "ja": "まだ？",
          "en": "Not yet?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 43,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "飾るよ",
          "en": "I'll put it up."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 44,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "きれい",
          "en": "Beautiful"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 45,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "涼しいですね",
          "en": "It's cool, isn't it?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 46,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "七夕　晴れてよかったですね",
          "en": "It's great that the weather is clear for Tanabata, isn't it?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "はい",
          "en": "Yes."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}